{
  "stem": "18470.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My mother said, under no circumstances am I going to bury myself in some [NON-ENGLISH] town as she called it, in South Carolina that she had never been to.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[LAUGHTER] And then, you know, another thing my-- my dad tried also to get a job as a cantor, because he knew the liturgy.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He had a nice voice, but not an operatic voice.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And one day [SIGHS] he told me the story about-- this was in the eight months when he was trying to find his-- his way here.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He went to a place called Cop Girardo to try out to be a cantor.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they were just miserable to him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he kept talking about what nasty people these people in Cop Girardo were.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So one day I'm flying on an airplane, and I pull out and an air map.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm just looking.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I say, oh my god, there's Cop Girardo, Cape Girardeau, Missouri.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It became Cop Girardo.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHTER]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, you know, it was they didn't know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's why I have such great empathy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The other day I met with three Russian immigrants, who've been in Cincinnati for five years.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One spoke and wrote poetry in English.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because he had learned English in school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "One man who was a woodworker, could understand but couldn't speak.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the third spoke to me in Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I-- I said, you've got here replicated in a different generation what immigration was like in the '30s.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It wasn't just German Jews, but Jews who escaped Eastern Europe.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Non-Jews who came and got out had the same kind of struggle.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they grouped in the same neighborhoods.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's why they held together, because there was some security in the restricted neighborhoods.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my-- my society was restricted too.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
